{"tid":2047752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藏摺刀被控管有攻擊性武器 控方未能證意圖 男生受審即日脫罪","createTime":"2020-06-02T10:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T01:48:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f771cca82cfe142ed6c0c4f38394b1f91cb3e566","tid":2047752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/Y7SPVP5FCMYPQGYEXDMJUBNFBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FY7SPVP5FCMYPQGYEXDMJUBNFBU%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=fba7eae8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FY7SPVP5FCMYPQGYEXDMJUBNFBU%2F&h=aed3f58d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/Y7SPVP5FCMYPQGYEXDMJUBNFBU/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年11月20日發起「和你塞」活動，港鐵灣仔站有列車車門被阻擋，不能關上。有休班警介入並與現場人士爭執，被指「郁手打人，仲要打幾個」，休班警則回應「費時同你哋拗，等警察嚟」。及後有其他警員接報到場，在站內一名患專注失調及過度活躍症的男生背囊內發現摺刀。男生被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，今日受審，庭上自言是愛刀之人，視刀為護身符及藝術品。裁判官即日裁決，直指被告說法是天方夜譚，但即使他藏有摺刀，也不能證明他必然有意圖用刀傷害他人，故裁定罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"d7fe9a146a180da3fca31d098912b771e05300c2","tid":2047752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T10:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d4645f48512d61dbdd0bea638496bc0c470c05","tid":2047752,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"